    dc:title "On new or poorly known Australian Filistatidae spiders (Araneae: Araneomorphae), including a study on the fine morphology of Wandella" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.269081>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.269082>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.269083>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.269080> ;
